This is the index page of pico zola theme.
Lightweight and clean. Built on top of simple grid
See some useful info in features page

https://salif.github.io/zola-themes-coll.body:
General
I am not the best webmaster, but should be somewhat responsive.
I intentionally using the bigger fonts to make, feel free to change it in main.css
Light mode
Now light mode also supported.
Important
Please make sure to set up your base_url with trailing slash:

Comments
Theme supports Giscuss for comments. The configuration is done via config.toml. Here you can see the example section used for this page deployment:

Page configurations
Customize the page blocks by setting configuration in [extra] section:

Blog
I am using this theme for my notes, or probably blog.
The section template supports pagination, tags, sorts the pages by publication date. You may see the working example here
Search
The theme supports the search using elasticrunrjs. To enable the search, you will need the following configuration in config.toml:

config.toml extras
